title: The Smiths: 8 Albums (MP3 Format)
description:
The other eight-album collection was in .ogg format, so I fixed it and now it is in .mp3 format. Enjoy.

\&#039;The Smiths: 8 Albums\&#039; includes:

 - Hatful of Hollow **
 - Louder than Bombs **
 - Meat is Murder *
 - Rank **
 - Strangeways, Here We Come *
 - The Queen is Dead *
 - The Smiths (Self-Titled Debut Album) *

* denotes studio album
** denotes compilation album

I will seed this for as long as possible. After that, it\&#039;s all up to you.
